  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "chapterTitle": "The National Education Service",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN_20_38403-38630",
          "range": "38403-38630",
          "rangeStart": 38403,
          "rangeEnd": 38630,
          "markText": "I was getting seriously angry at these facetious and unworthy answers. ‘We’re supposed to be educating them for a working life and three-quarters of the time they’re bored stiff.’\n",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1748009139,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-05-23 22:05:39",
          "chapterUid": 20,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=38403&rangeEnd=38630",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e1142093643425f434b6438476c384a41437267367743367837334a3239644ed22?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=38403&rangeEnd=38630"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN_20_38738-38873",
          "range": "38738-38873",
          "rangeStart": 38738,
          "rangeEnd": 38873,
          "markText": "‘I should have thought being bored stiff for three-quarters of the time was excellent preparation for working life,’ was the flip reply",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1748009125,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-05-23 22:05:25",
          "chapterUid": 20,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=38738&rangeEnd=38873",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e1142093643425f434b6438476c384a41437267367743367837334a3239644ed22?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=38738&rangeEnd=38873"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN_20_39013-39135",
          "range": "39013-39135",
          "rangeStart": 39013,
          "rangeEnd": 39135,
          "markText": "‘Humphrey,’ I said firmly, ‘we raised the leaving age to sixteen to enable them to learn more. And they’re learning less.’",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1748009121,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-05-23 22:05:21",
          "chapterUid": 20,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=39013&rangeEnd=39135",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e1142093643425f434b6438476c384a41437267367743367837334a3239644ed22?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=39013&rangeEnd=39135"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN_20_39282-39470",
          "range": "39282-39470",
          "rangeStart": 39282,
          "rangeEnd": 39470,
          "markText": "Suddenly he answered me seriously. ‘We didn’t raise the leaving age to enable them to learn more. We raised it to keep teenagers off the job market and hold down the unemployment figures.’",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1748008617,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-05-23 21:56:57",
          "chapterUid": 20,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=39282&rangeEnd=39470",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e1142093643425f434b6438476c384a41437267367743367837334a3239644ed22?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=39282&rangeEnd=39470"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "chapterTitle": "Official Secrets",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN_14_77566-77740",
          "range": "77566-77740",
          "rangeStart": 77566,
          "rangeEnd": 77740,
          "markText": "8. Take Refuge in a Long Pointless Narrative. If you can ramble on for long enough, no one will remember the question and therefore no one can tell if you answered it or not.",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1748009069,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-05-23 22:04:29",
          "chapterUid": 14,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=77566&rangeEnd=77740",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e1142093643425f434b6438476c384a41437267367743367837334a3239644ed22?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=77566&rangeEnd=77740"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN_14_77156-77392",
          "range": "77156-77392",
          "rangeStart": 77156,
          "rangeEnd": 77392,
          "markText": "7. Invoke Secrecy. ‘There’s a very full answer to that question, but it involves matters that are being discussed in confidence. I’m sure you wouldn’t want me to break a confidence. So I’m afraid I can’t answer for another week or two.’",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1748009063,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-05-23 22:04:23",
          "chapterUid": 14,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=77156&rangeEnd=77392",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e1142093643425f434b6438476c384a41437267367743367837334a3239644ed22?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=77156&rangeEnd=77392"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN_14_76499-76924",
          "range": "76499-76924",
          "rangeStart": 76499,
          "rangeEnd": 76924,
          "markText": "6. Use The Time Factor. Most interviews are short of time, especially live ‘on air’ interviews. Reply: ‘That’s a very interesting question, and there are nine points that I should like to make in answer to it.’ The Interviewer will say: ‘Perhaps you could make just two of them, briefly.’ You say: ‘No, it’s far too important a question to answer superficially, and if I can’t answer it properly I’d rather not trivialise it.",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1748009055,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-05-23 22:04:15",
          "chapterUid": 14,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=76499&rangeEnd=76924",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e1142093643425f434b6438476c384a41437267367743367837334a3239644ed22?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=76499&rangeEnd=76924"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN_14_76053-76321",
          "range": "76053-76321",
          "rangeStart": 76053,
          "rangeEnd": 76321,
          "markText": "5. Make It All Appear An Act. This approach only works for live TV interviews: ‘You know, I’ve come to the conclusion that I don’t agree with what you suggested I should answer when you asked me that question downstairs before the programme began. The real answer is …",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1748009051,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-05-23 22:04:11",
          "chapterUid": 14,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=76053&rangeEnd=76321",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e1142093643425f434b6438476c384a41437267367743367837334a3239644ed22?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=76053&rangeEnd=76321"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN_14_75755-75950",
          "range": "75755-75950",
          "rangeStart": 75755,
          "rangeEnd": 75950,
          "markText": "b) ‘Surely in a nation of 56 million people you can find a few people who will say anything, no matter how irrelevant, misguided, or ill-informed.’\n",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1748009046,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-05-23 22:04:06",
          "chapterUid": 14,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=75755&rangeEnd=75950",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e1142093643425f434b6438476c384a41437267367743367837334a3239644ed22?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=75755&rangeEnd=75950"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN_14_75632-75645",
          "range": "75632-75645",
          "rangeStart": 75632,
          "rangeEnd": 75645,
          "markText": "a) ‘Name ten.",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1748009040,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-05-23 22:04:00",
          "chapterUid": 14,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=75632&rangeEnd=75645",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e1142093643425f434b6438476c384a41437267367743367837334a3239644ed22?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=75632&rangeEnd=75645"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN_14_75244-75509",
          "range": "75244-75509",
          "rangeStart": 75244,
          "rangeEnd": 75509,
          "markText": "4. Unloading The Question. Most questions are loaded. They are full of assumptions such as ‘A lot of people have said that you consider yourself above the law’. There are two possible replies to such loaded questions:\n",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1748009034,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-05-23 22:03:54",
          "chapterUid": 14,
