    {
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "chapterTitle": "A Conflict of Interest",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN_16_42369-42715",
          "range": "42369-42715",
          "rangeStart": 42369,
          "rangeEnd": 42715,
          "markText": "Sir Humphrey found it no deterrent that the PM was keen on Jameson. In fact, he seemed to regard it as a positive bonus. ‘That will be my starting point. If you want to suggest that someone is perhaps not the ideal choice [i.e. rubbish them – Ed.], the first stage is to express absolute support.’\n",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1748008982,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-05-23 22:03:02",
          "chapterUid": 16,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=42369&rangeEnd=42715",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e1142093643425f434b6438476c384a41437267367743367837334a3239644ed22?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=42369&rangeEnd=42715"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN_16_44737-44939",
          "range": "44737-44939",
          "rangeStart": 44737,
          "rangeEnd": 44939,
          "markText": "Stage Three is simply done, I learned that day, by oversimplificaton. You label someone. If, for instance, someone is a good man he can seriously be damaged by calling him ‘Mr Clean’. Strange, but true.",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1748008949,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-05-23 22:02:29",
          "chapterUid": 16,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=44737&rangeEnd=44939",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e1142093643425f434b6438476c384a41437267367743367837334a3239644ed22?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=44737&rangeEnd=44939"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN_16_44544-44611",
          "range": "44544-44611",
          "rangeStart": 44544,
          "rangeEnd": 44611,
          "markText": "Stage Four: Mention his bad points by defending and excusing them.’",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1748008937,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-05-23 22:02:17",
          "chapterUid": 16,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_CKd8Gl8JACrg6wC6x73J29dN&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=44544&rangeEnd=44611",
